 at Menado, Celebes, Dutch East Indies.</td></tr><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/01/12/1942' alt='See all events on 12 Jan 1942' title='See all events on 12 Jan 1942' class='noStyle'>12 Jan 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nachi arrived at Ominato Guard District, Mutsu, Aomori Prefecture, Japan at 0715 hours.</td></tr><tr bgcolor=''><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/01/24/1942' alt='See all events on 24 Jan 1942' title='See all events on 24 Jan 1942' class='noStyle'>24 Jan 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nachi provided support for the landings at Kendari, Celebes, Dutch East Indies.</td></tr><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/01/29/1942' alt='See all events on 29 Jan 1942' title='See all events on 29 Jan 1942' class='noStyle'>29 Jan 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nachi departed Davao, Philippine Islands for Bangka Roads, Celebes, Dutch East Indies.</td></tr><tr bgcolor=''><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/02/05/1942' alt='See all events on 5 Feb 1942' title='See all events on 5 Feb 1942' class='noStyle'>5 Feb 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nachi departed Bangka Roads, Celebes, Dutch East Indies to support the landings at Makassar, Celebes.</td></tr><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/02/17/1942' alt='See all events on 17 Feb 1942' title='See all events on 17 Feb 1942' class='noStyle'>17 Feb 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nachi provided support for the landings at Dili, Portuguese Timor.</td></tr><tr bgcolor=''><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/02/24/1942' alt='See all events on 24 Feb 1942' title='See all events on 24 Feb 1942' class='noStyle'>24 Feb 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nachi departed Staring Bay, Celebes, Dutch East Indies with Cruiser Division 5.</td></tr><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/02/27/1942' alt='See all events on 27 Feb 1942' title='